  <official_title>Role of 3 Tesla Diffusion Weighted Magnetic Resonance Imaging (DW-MRI) for Diagnosis Bladder Cancer Grade and Stage. Potential Role of the Apparent Diffusion Coefficient (ADC) Value</official_title>
