  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      assess diagnostic performance of 3-Tesla DW-MRI in detecting and staging bladder cancer and
      potential role of the ADC value as a biomarker reflecting histological grade and stage.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
